_sText:
This map is compatible for Gun Game (it has buy zones), Aim, and Fy. The whole map is made out of displacements, and it has HDR.

I am happy to hear any Complaints or Suggestions, and of course, positive feedback. 

Do not decompile or edit in any way without my permission. I may be making a few versions of this map, so stay tuned. 

If you want to put it on your server please tell me! Because I'll stop by and play!

The maximum players are 25 on 25, but I prefer a smaller game of 10 on 10. But please be free to try more. 

Have fun, and play hard!

Currently running on this server IP: 85.234.148.18:29025

UPDATE:
IF YOU DOWNLOADED THIS MAP PREVIOUS TO TUESDAY, APRIL 24TH, THEN DELETE THE 2 EXTRA FILES (THE ZTMP FILES) THAT CAME WITH THE MAP! THEY CREATE PROBLEMS WHEN PEOPLE DOWNLOAD THE MAP OFF OF A SERVER.
